description: Quick to make and packed with flavour and a touch of smokiness.
name: Plant Based 'Chicken' Skewers with Capsicum, Onions, Rosemary & Garlic Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 small red capsicum, de-seeded and cut into chunks
1 small green capsicum, de-seeded and cut into chunks
1 small white onion, peeled and cut into chunks
1 small red onion, peeled and cut into chunks

recipeInstructions.text: Heat up a chargrill to a medium heat. Add the plant-based chicken and vegetables onto skewers. Chargrill the skewers for 10 minutes while rotating.
